A motorcyclist has been seriously injured in a crash in Kent.Emergency services were called to the crash involving a motorcycle and a green Range Rover on the A257 at about 13:00 BST on Friday.The collision happened between Littlebourne and Wingham, near the junction with Cherville Lane, Kent Police said.The motorcyclist was flown to a London hospital where he remains in a serious but stable condition.
Anyone who witnessed the crash between Canterbury and Sandwich or who has dashcam footage is urged to contact police.
